    {
      "title": "<span id=\"#28622\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">congratulate</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(v.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>\"慰问和表达同情的高兴之情的称呼\"，来源于1540年代的拉丁语  <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">congratulatus</span>，过去分词形式的  <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">congratulari</span>  “祝愿快乐”，来自于 assimilated 形式的  <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">com</span>  “一起，与”（见  <a href=\"/cn/word/con-\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of con- \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\">con-</a> ）和  <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">gratulari</span>  “表示感谢，表达高兴之情”， 来自  <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">gratus</span>  “愉快的”（源自于 PIE 词根  <a href=\"/cn/word/*gwere-#etymonline_v_53052\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of *gwere- \" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"crossreference notranslate\">*gwere-</a> (2) “支持”的 suffixed 形式）。相关词语： <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">Congratulated</span>； <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">congratulating; congratulable</span> 。</p><ins class=\"adsbygoogle relative inline-block transition-all inline-block h-[250px] w-[300px]\" data-ad-slot=\"4000736339\" data-adtest=\"off\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"></ins>"
    }
  ],
