    {
      "title": "congratulatory<div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(adj.)</div>",
      "html": "<p>\"表达祝贺\"，1520年代； 见 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of congratulate \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/congratulate\">congratulate</a> + <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of -ory \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/-ory\">-ory</a>。</p>"
